VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(password|passwd|secret|api_key|apikey|token|access_key)\s*=\s*['"]?[A-Za-z0-9@#$%^&*!_\-]{8,}['"]?
WHEN EXPR MISSING:vault|secret_manager|\$\{.*\}
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects hardcoded credentials or secrets assigned as shell variables.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Hardcoded Credential in Shell Script.
